Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:06.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I had no idea there were so many \Ndifferent stalls for New Year's!}Năm mới có nhiều gian hàng mở ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:11.49,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I've only ever been to smaller shrines, \Nso I've never seen anything like this before.}Em chỉ mới đi mấy ngôi đền nhỏ, \Nđây là lần đầu đến đền lớn đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san, look! \NThey've got a shooting game!}Shinozaki, nhìn kìa! Có game bắn súng đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.81,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Chị xin lỗi... chị hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.08,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{No, please, don't worry about it!}Không không có gì ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.38,0:00:31.09,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm making such a fuss, \Nmy kohai is going to think I'm childish.}Mình lại tỏ ra háo hức như \Ncon nít trước mặt đàn em rồi...
