Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:41.94,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Do you think she's lost?}Em ấy bị lạc à?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:43.23,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe.}Có thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.07,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.98,0:00:48.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Where are your parents?}Ba mẹ em đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.58,Main,Girl,0,0,0,,{I dunno...}Em không biết...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:54.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You were very brave \Nto hang in there on your own.}Em đã cố gắng lắm rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:00.49,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'll stay with you now, so don't worry.}Chị sẽ ở cùng em nên là an tâm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.38,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Looks like she is lost.}Có vẻ con bé bị lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.98,0:01:13.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That was really mature of you, Senpai.}Chị trưởng thành ghê đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, of course! I'm an adult, after all.}Ủa? Chị là người lớn mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.64,0:01:21.17,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{They've got a station for lost kids \Nat the reception desk, right?}Hình như ở ga có chỗ giữ trẻ lạc.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.17,0:01:22.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah! Let's go.}Vâng! Đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:26.21,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Look there, Yutaka-san.}Nhìn đi Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.03,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{They look like parents \Nwith their child, don't they?!}Bọn họ cứ như hai vợ chồng ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.58,0:01:35.76,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I can see it... my cute little sister, \Nand her cute little daughter!}Tôi có thể thấy... em gái dễ thương và con gái...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.76,0:01:38.21,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Would you two stop fussing? It's childish.}Hai người đừng trẻ con nữa được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:46.10,Italics - Top,Lyrics,0,0,0,,{Oh, I love you so much, I just have to laugh}
