Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:12.64,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Time to start a new year of work.}Hôm nay là bắt đầu công việc lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.86,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Good morning!}Chào buổi sáng
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:18.02,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's a pleasure to be \Nworking with you again, Senpai!}Hôm nay lại mong chị chỉ bảo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:25.00,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hearing you call me that makes me \Nfeel like it's time to get back to work.}Nghe em nói thế chị cảm giác \Nbắt đầu năm mới được rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.72,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{If you like it, I can call you that \Nwhenever you like!}Nếu chị muốn thì em sẽ nói mỗi ngày.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.48,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{I have to say, New Year's went \Nby in the blink of an eye.}Cơ mà kì nghỉ qua nhanh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:35.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Considering you were a student last year, \Nit probably seems even faster.}Năm ngoái em vẫn còn là sinh viên \Nnên cảm thấy vậy là dĩ nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:39.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I feel like...}Cảm giác như...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:44.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{the angle at which I'm looking up at \NShinozaki-san is different from usual...}góc mình nhìn lên Shinozaki có vẻ khác mọi khi...
