Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:54.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When I would see him before, \Nmy head was around here.}Lúc trước mình đứng cỡ này...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.52,0:03:57.25,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Now I'm a little higher...}Giờ lại cao hơn xíu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:03:59.86,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Could it be?}Không có lẽ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.01,0:04:04.21,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Have I gotten taller?!}Mình đã cao lên?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.35,0:04:06.64,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.50,0:04:14.90,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm a little different \Nthan usual today. Can you tell?}Hôm nay em thấy chị có gì khác không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{She's different?}Khác hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.37,0:04:20.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,Quần áo với giày cũng khác.{\i1}{Her clothes and shoes are different,}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:25.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but I don't think she'd ask \Nif it was something that obvious...}Nhưng chắc không phải ý chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.25,0:04:31.20,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Standard practice is to check nails, \Nbut those don't seem different...}Hay là làm móng mới? Có vẻ không phải...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.96,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You can't tell?}Em không biết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.15,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{This scent...}Mùi hương...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:40.27,Italics,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's it!}Chính nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.37,0:04:43.63,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Did you switch to a different shampoo?}Chị đổi mùi dầu gọi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:48.10,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Có đổi nhưng không phải cái đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:52.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I got it wrong! A pervert! \NShe'll think I'm a pervert!}Mình hiểu nhầm rồi! Mình là thằng biến thái!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:57.13,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san... \Nyou've been smelling my shampoo?}Shinozaki... em lúc nào cũng ngửi chị à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It's not like that, Senpai!}Không phải đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I swear, it wasn't anything untoward...}Em thề... là chỉ ngẫu nhiên thôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.36,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'll need to be careful with my \Nshampoo choices going forward...}Lần tới phải chọn dầu gội cẩn thận hơn...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:09.87,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{He seems really stumped.}Em ấy có vẻ bối rối.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.37,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I should give him an obvious hint.}Phải cho em ấy gợi ý.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.30,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay, here's a hint.}Gợi ý nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:21.89,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's not my hair or anything in particular \Nlike that, but more my body as a whole.}Không phải tóc hay mấy cái cụ thể. \NMà là toàn bộ cơ thể.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.77,0:05:24.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Your whole body?}Toàn bộ cơ thể á?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.90,0:05:28.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Her whole... body...}Toàn bộ... cơ thể...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:35.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I just told my kohai \Nto pay attention to my body!}Mình vừa nói đàn em là hãy nhìn vào cơ thể?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:39.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{That's what you're into, huh?}Chị có sở thích đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:42.78,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A pervert! He'll think I'm a pervert!}Em ấy sẽ nghĩ mình biến thái mất!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:48.28,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{H-How about another hint?}G-Gợi ý khác không ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.71,0:05:50.28,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{L-Let's see...}Để xem nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.72,0:05:54.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Well, there's a big size difference between us.}Khác nhau về sự phát triển giữa hai ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.54,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{That should make it pretty clear.}Thế này thì em hiểu rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A size difference... Th-Then maybe...}Sự phát triển... giữa hai ta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.81,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{You mean to say they've gotten even bigger?!}Tức là chúng to hơn rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.93,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Did you figure it out?}Em biết là gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.84,0:06:10.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It can't be that!}Chuyện đó có hơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well... I give up.}Em chịu thua.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:18.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Okay, here's the answer.}Câu trả lời nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.19,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It turns out...}Đó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:24.97,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Ta-da! I'm a little bit taller!}Chiều cao của chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:29.30,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Now that you mention it, \Nyou do seem a bit taller...}Nhắc mới thấy. Có vẻ cao hơn xíu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:33.70,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{The boots... That explains it.}Giày... ra là thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:37.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, you're wearing \Nboots for a change, after all.}Hôm nay chị đi bốt cao gót nhỉ.
