Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I'm just gonna sit here \Nfor the rest of the day.}Hôm nay chị sẽ ngồi yên ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.98,Main,Shionozaki,0,0,0,,{But maybe you did get a bit taller!}Nhưng có thể chị có cao lên mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:51.51,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{You don't need to humor me.}Không cần thương hại đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well... Senpai...}Chị ơi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:57.47,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I thought I was getting taller... Sulk...}Chị cứ nghĩ mình cao lên...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.98,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-kun!}Shinozaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.06,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.98,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{I've got something I'd like you \Nto take care of today...}Hôm nay có chuyện cần nhờ cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.98,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HF2F7F6&\bord0\shad0\blur2\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(553,300)}m 0 0 l 140 0 l 140 75 l 0 75
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.48,0:07:05.98,sign_4975_56_Days_Earlier,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fscy140\bord0\q2\fs16\pos(553,300)}{Public Relations\N}{\fs22}{Ishiyama Satoshi}Quan hệ công chúng\N Satoshi Ishiyama
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:12.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Well, Katase-san oversees my scheduling, \Nso you'll need to talk to her.}Chị Katase quản lý lịch của\N em nên anh hãy hỏi chị ấy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.99,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Don't be like that, Shinozaki-kun.}Cậu chẳng hiểu gì cả, Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:16.69,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{They do say, "when you're young,}Họ thường nói "Khi còn trẻ,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.69,0:07:18.75,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{you should tackle \Nas many challenges as you can!"}hãy thử thách bản thân nhiều lên!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:21.76,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Pwease?}Làm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.75,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Making a cute face doesn't change the answer!}Tỏ ra dễ thương cũng chẳng thay đổi được gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.75,0:07:25.50,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Unfortunately for you,}Đáng tiếc,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:30.76,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{we're not in the habit of accepting challenges \Nthat don't actually serve a purpose.}là bên tôi không nhận những thử thách\N không liên quan đến chuyên môn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.45,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Katase-san!}Katase!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.51,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai.}Chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:36.03,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{I-I thought you were in a meeting...}T-Tưởng cậu đang họp...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:40.52,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Oh, so you asked Shinozaki-san about this \Nbecause you thought I wasn't around?}Ý cậu là lợi dụng lúc tôi đi họp để nhờ vả?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.52,0:07:43.20,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Catch you next time, Shinozaki-kun!}Gặp sau nhé Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:46.45,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Ishiyama-kun never changes, does he?}Ishiyama chẳng thay đổi gì cả.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.29,0:07:50.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{An internal email?}Email?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.53,Sign_Basic,E-mail Sign,0,0,0,,{\c&H4E5147&\3c&HD5DACF&\shad0\fs20\an6\pos(268,104)}{Sender:}
