Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.53,Sign_Basic,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{\c&H4E5147&\3c&HF5FAF2&\shad0\fs24\an4\pos(196.667,282)}{Wanna do it in secret?}Bí mật làm nó nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.88,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Wanna do it in secret?!}Bí mật làm nó nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.53,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{He doesn't give up!}Vẫn chưa từ bỏ à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:55.80,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hiss!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.41,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Hiss! Hiss! Hiss! Hiss!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Please stop trying to assign work \Ndirectly to my subordinates!}Đừng có sai vặt cấp dưới của người khác nữa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:04.40,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{But you wouldn't do it, Katase-san...}Nhưng không cho mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{I never said I wouldn't!}Có ai nói không làm đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.58,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{But if you need something done,}Nhưng nếu có chuyện gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:13.18,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{you need to talk to me first, \Nso we can do things properly.}thì phải bàn với tôi trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:16.68,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{You mean it?!}Thật hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.35,0:08:19.43,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{In that case, I was wondering...}Nếu vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:23.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Katase-san really is quite the reliable senpai.}Em ấy đáng tin cậy ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.79,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Okay.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:21.77,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{I see...}Hiểu rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:26.68,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\an8}{This should be doable \Nif we adjust the schedule.}Nếu điều chỉnh lại lịch thế này...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.69,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.02,Main,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Really?! Thank you!}Thật sao? Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{How'd your fortune turn out, Senpai?}Chị bốc được quẻ gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.33,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Not telling.}Bí mật.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.91,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My Tiny Senpai}{\i0}{.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.73,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm still not used to being \N here at night...}Mình vẫn chưa quen nổi làm đêm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.51,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Whatcha doing?}Em làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:09:01.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My boss can seem to appear out of thin air.}Quản lý lúc nào cũng xuất hiện từ hư không.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:05.03,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{D-Don't scare me like that! \NI thought you were a ghost or something.}Đừng có hù em chứ! Cứ tưởng ma quỷ!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Sorry, sorry.}Xin lỗi xin lỗi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.63,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{But why are you working late \Nby yourself if you're scared?}Nhưng em sợ vậy rồi sao còn ở lại làm đêm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:11.90,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Were you really that busy?}Em bận đến thế hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:14.40,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well...}Chuyện này...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:16.31,Flashback,Ishiyama,0,0,0,,{Pwease?}Làm ơn?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.89,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Ishiyama-san in PR said \Nhe needed this tomorrow...}Anh Ishiyama nói cần nó vào sáng mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:24.49,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Did he get approval from \Nyour supervisor for this?}Đã được cho phép bởi cấp trên của em chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.31,0:09:27.30,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san...}Hayakawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:29.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I know, I know!}Em biết rồi mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:32.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{He asked me right at the end of the day}Tại anh ấy hỏi em vào gần cuối giờ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.84,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{and said there was no one else \Nhe could turn to.}và nói rằng chỉ có em mới cứu được...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.85,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Even so, fundamentally speaking, you really \Nshouldn't accept assignments on your own.}Dù là thế thì em cũng \Nkhông nên nhận thêm việc đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Especially since you're new. Ask first.}Em là người mới nên phải báo cáo trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:43.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:46.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{But I thought, if I could just \Nget it done in secret...}Nhưng em nghĩ nếu lén lút làm thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:47.41,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Still no.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.77,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{That'd just mean he's taking advantage \Nof how nice you are, Hayakawa-san.}Làm thế sẽ cho cậu ta dễ lợi dụng em hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:10:01.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{And speaking as a manager, \Nit's not nice at all!}Và nói đến quản lý thì cũng chẳng tốt lành gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:03.29,Main,Hayakwa,0,0,0,,{You're completely right.}Anh nói phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.61,0:10:06.29,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'll have a word with Ishiyama-kun.}Tôi sẽ làm việc với Ishiyama sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.29,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Sorry about all this...}Em xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.69,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Well, it's part of the job.}Thôi, cũng là công việc của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:11.83,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Um...}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:16.61,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I really appreciate it.}Em cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.14,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{What?! What's wrong?! You okay?!}Sao thế? Em sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.57,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Sorry...}Em xin lỗi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:28.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's just, having someone looking out \Nfor me... made me so glad, y'know?}Chỉ là... không ngờ có người quan tâm đến em...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.63,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It's a real relief.}Cảm giác thật nhẹ nhõm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.13,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{One second.}Chờ tôi chút.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:37.45,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.82,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn anh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Have you eaten anything?}Đã ăn gì chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:47.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{It was a rush job, so...}Tại gấp gáp quá nên...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:49.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{How much longer do you think it'll be?}Còn cỡ bao lâu nữa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:51.85,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I just need to submit it and I'll be done.}Em đang chỉnh sửa lại thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{So fast!}Nhanh thế!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.09,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{If you've got time, \Ndo you wanna grab something to eat?}Nếu vậy thì đi kiếm gì ăn không?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.09,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{You sure?}Thật ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:01.82,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Consider it a little reward \Nfor a hard worker who made a mistake.}Là phần thưởng cho sự cố gắng của em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:08.47,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{How can he just say stuff like that...?}Sao anh lại nói câu đó nhẹ tênh vậy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.51,0:11:15.52,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{The entrance made it look like \Nmodern residence,}Lối vào khá hiện đại,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.01,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{but it's got an old fashioned Japanese style.}nhưng bên trong lại là kiểu Nhật.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.11,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Kinda surprising, right?}Khá là ngạc nhiên nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.24,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Tempting to just space out, taking it in.}Tôi cũng không ngờ đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.99,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What?! Why did he just sit next to me?}Hả? Sao lại ngồi cạnh mình?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.48,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this a move?}Anh ấy cố tình hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.48,0:11:29.71,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is he pulling some kind of move on me?!}Định làm gì mình sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:31.00,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H010301&\3c&HFAFBF8&\shad2\fs20\pos(218,185)}{*Not really\Nthinking about it}Không quan tâm
