Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:34.00,Main,Sign; top 3 headings,0,0,0,,{\fad(425,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\shad0\c&H586364&\3c&HE2F0F0&\an9\fs18\frx36\fry348\frz6.203\fax-.3\pos(432.666,108.666)}{Non-alcoholic}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:34.00,Sign_Basic,Sign; top 3 headings,0,0,0,,{\fad(375,0)\fnTimes New Roman\b1\shad0\c&H586364&\3c&HE2F0F0&\an9\fs18\frx36\fry348\frz6.203\fax-.3\pos(568.667,70)}{Drink Menu}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.47,0:11:34.00,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What a big non-alcoholic selection!}Nhiều thức uống không cồn ghê!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:37.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I had no idea there was somewhere \Nlike this so close to the office.\N}Không ngờ gần công ty lại có quán này.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:41.76,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I noticed you almost never drink \Nwhen we have drinking parties,}Tôi thấy em ít khi uống trong mấy bữa tiệc công ty,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.13,0:11:44.26,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{so I thought you might enjoy it a bit more.}nên thỉnh thoảng hãy cứ thả lỏng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:47.42,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Are you trying to be the ideal guy right now?}Anh ấy định làm người tốt à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:51.45,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{What percentage of the office \Nhas confessed to you before?}Trước đây có ai từng tỏ tình với anh chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:53.33,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Not }{\i1}{that}{\i0}{ many!}Cũng không nhiều lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Didn't deny that he's been approached, though.}Anh ấy không phủ nhận à...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.29,0:12:02.13,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Manager... you never really talk about \Nyour romantic history, do you?}Quản lý... anh chưa từng nói về \Nchuyện tình cảm bản thân nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.21,0:12:05.18,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No one really asks.}Thì có ai hỏi đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.79,0:12:08.87,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{If I asked...}Nếu em hỏi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.33,0:12:12.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{If I asked, would you tell me?}Anh có nói không?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.35,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{You wanna know?}Em muốn biết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.43,0:12:21.90,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{I don't mean anything untoward by it!}E-Em không có ý gì mờ ám đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:23.58,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Untoward how?}Mờ ám gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:25.93,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this just him? Is he just a ditz...?}Anh ấy... ngây thơ quá vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.95,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Romance, huh...?}Tình cảm à...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:34.62,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{When I was younger, I didn't really \Nunderstand how it felt to like someone.}Hồi còn nhỏ, tôi không\N hiểu lắm về cảm xúc thích ai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:37.71,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I tried dating quite a few times \Nup through college,}Tôi đã cố thử hẹn hò với vài người hồi lên đại học,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:40.97,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{but in the end, I never really found love.}nhưng cuối cùng chẳng thể tìm ra tình yêu đích thực.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.59,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I think my life might just be one \Nwith no romance to speak of.}Nên tôi nghĩ bản thân mình sẽ không thể có tình cảm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.71,0:12:48.86,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Manager...}Quản lý...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.09,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is that why?}Thế nên là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:53.08,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,{The thing is...}Tôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:59.09,Flashback,Akina,0,0,0,,{Nothing makes me happier than \Ncheering on someone else's love life.}Không có gì vui hơn khi ủng hộ tình yêu của ai đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:04.62,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{I'm more curious about your \Nromantic history, Hayakawa-san!}Quan trọng hơn là em cơ, chuyện tình cảm của em!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.65,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{M-Me...?}E-Em á...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:09.25,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Now that reaction makes me curious!}Phản ứng đó đáng ngờ ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.05,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Oho.}Ô chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.45,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I thought I recognized that voice.}Tưởng ai chứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.60,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Yutaka-san!}Yutaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.16,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Is your office around here?}Công ty cô gần đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:20.86,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Indeed. In the opposite direction of \Nthe station, though, so it's a bit of a walk.}Ừm, ngược lại nhà ga nên tôi đi bộ hơi xa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.75,0:13:25.36,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Some coworkers dragged me this way, \Nbut I've never been one for big groups.}Nhưng vài đồng nghiệp nài nỉ nên tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.37,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{So I slipped out, but then realized...}Sau đó tôi lủi mất...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:30.88,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{It's lonely to be on your own!}Và cảm thấy cô đơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.88,0:13:31.87,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{\i1}{So free-spirited!}Tự do tự tại quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:35.28,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{That being the case, \Nwould you mind if I joined you?}Thế nên cho tôi tham gia cùng nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.21,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Go ahead.}Vâng!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:39.81,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{If you'll excuse me...}Vậy thì xin phép...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.47,0:13:43.00,Main - Top,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Gimme pics of Shiorin!}Gửi ảnh Shiorin đây nào!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.37,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Come on, what am I getting so anxious about?}S-Sao mình lại ghen tị chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:44.97,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Ask to your brother.}Hỏi em trai cô ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.45,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Besides, I don't have any.}Với cả tôi không có chụp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.37,0:13:48.89,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{All she did was sit \Nin an empty seat, normally...}Chị ấy chỉ ngồi ở ghế trống thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:48.00,Main - Top,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{\an8}{Is that right?}Thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:48.89,Main - Top,Akina,0,0,0,,{\an8}{It is.}Phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.66,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Normally...}Bình thường...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.51,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Chika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:57.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I think I'll sit here instead.}Quả nhiên tôi ngồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:00.28,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Just sit across the table \Nlike a normal person!}Làm ơn ngồi bên kia đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:01.02,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Don't wanna.}Không thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.49,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I could see a wish for me to \Nsit here in those eyes.}Chị có thể thấy ánh mắt muốn mình ngồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:04.86,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Whose?!}Mắt ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.86,0:14:05.96,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Yours.}Em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:06.96,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{Well, you're wrong!}Em không có!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:07.82,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I saw it.}Có.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.91,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{I guess... she didn't want to sit next to me.}Chị... không muốn ngồi cạnh em ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.29,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll sit here, after all.}Quả nhiên chị sẽ ngồi đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.33,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{O-Onee-san...}Chị...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.71,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{In that case, I'll just sit over here.}Vậy thì anh ngồi bên này.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.17,0:14:24.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{You should sit here, Manager.}Anh nên ngồi bên kia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.96,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{No, no, that's for you, Yutaka-san.}Không không, là cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:26.97,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{No, no...}Không không...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:29.09,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{\i1}{What's with these two?}Bọn họ bị gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.34,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Hayakawa-san.}Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.60,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,Chika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:34.60,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{If I'm interrupting, \NI'll head on home, so let me know.}Nếu thấy cản trở thì tôi (chị) sẽ về nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.45,Main,Haykawa,0,0,0,,{Both of you sit down over there!}Cả hai ngồi bên kia đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:41.19,Main,Both,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.81,Main,Hyakawa,0,0,0,,{Unbelievable...}Thiệt tình...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.81,0:14:44.61,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{You're really pouring it back, Chika-chan!}Em uống dữ quá Chika-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.61,0:14:46.01,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Are you a big drinker?}Tiên tửu hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.14,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,{This is nonalcoholic!}Đây là đồ uống không cồn mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:48.92,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I see. Yet, you're still red.}Ra là vậy. Mặt em đỏ là do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:49.66,Main,Akina,0,0,0,,{Oh, my!}Chà!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.22,Main,Hayakawa,0,0,0,,Im đi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:14:58.55,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{My body feels heavy for some reason...}Cơ thể nặng quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.33,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Is this sleep paralysis?}Bị bóng đè à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.90,0:15:05.09,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Li'l Bro. Gimme some Shiorin-senpai pics.}Em trai. Đưa chị mày ảnh của Shiorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:11.59,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{It's just you?! And could you not barge \Ninto your brother's place on his day off?!}Chị à? Ngày nghỉ tự nhiên chui vào phòng \Nem trai mình lúc sáng sớm làm gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.14,0:15:13.97,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And... pictures of Senpai?}Ảnh của chị ấy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:17.47,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Correct. Shiorin's fluffiness \Nwon't leave my mind.}Ờ. Sự mềm mịn của Shiorin cứ trong tâm trí chị.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.24,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{I want to have a picture on hand \Nso I can air-fluff her at all times.}Chị muốn có hình ảnh để có thể tưởng tượng ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:22.60,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What kind of reason is that?!}Cái lý do gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.93,0:15:25.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And what are those hand movements?}Cơ mà tay chị làm gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:27.11,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Air-fluffing.}Bóp không khí.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:30.11,Flashback,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Yes, quite fluffy indeed.}Mềm mịn quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.11,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, that.}À...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:34.46,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Anyway, I don't have any pics \Nof Senpai in the first place.}Với cả em không có ảnh của chị ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:35.80,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Then get some.}Thế thì chụp đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.80,0:15:37.99,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You should ask Hayakawa instead.}Cái đó chị hỏi Hayakawa ấy.
