Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.28,0:15:40.50,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Your manager said to task you.}Nhiên tiện hỏi quản lý em luôn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:43.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Since when are you and my boss buddies?!}Chị làm gì mà thân với quản lý em thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.25,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Though, you're right...}Cơ mà chị nói đúng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:49.01,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could... show each other...}Chúng ta... sẽ cho nhau xem hả...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.01,0:15:52.76,Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,{We could send each other \Npictures of us wearing them!}Chúng ta có thể gửi ảnh mặc chúng cho nhau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:58.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We never did end up sending pics \Nof us wearing that loungewear...}Cuối cùng vẫn chưa trao đổi ảnh mặc đồ ngủ đôi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.13,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And I can't deny I'd like to see that...}Và mình cũng muốn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:03.37,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Yoink!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:05.55,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Sent!}Gửi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:07.77,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{What did you just send?!}Chị gửi cái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.53,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Something from Shinozaki-san?}Shinozaki gửi gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.48,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"I miss you on the weekend..."}Em nhớ chị quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:20.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Could you please send a picture \Nso I can see you whenever I want?"}Chị có thể gửi ảnh của mình cho em không?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:23.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Wh-Wh-Where did this\Ncome from all of a sudden?!}S-S-Sao tự nhiên lại?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:26.92,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{A-A-A-Am I dreaming?! \NAm I still asleep right now?!}M-Mình đang nằm mơ hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:31.55,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I should bathe first...}Phải tắm trước đã...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:34.21,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{My phone!}Điện thoại!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.35,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Okay, I've got it back.}Phù, lấy lại rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:40.18,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Great, it's already marked as read!}Chị ấy đọc rồi còn gì!
