Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.56,0:16:41.52,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Yay!}Ngon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:45.19,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Senpai, it's a trick! \NThat was my sister! I didn't say that!}Không phải! Chị em làm đó! Không phải em!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:49.94,Sign_Basic,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\an7\fs20\c&H5B5D51&\3c&HF4F7F4&\shad0\frz347.5\frx8\fry352\pos(236,200)}{I'm so sorry!\NMy sister sent that!\NYou can ignore it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.70,0:16:53.83,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{His sister? That explains it.}Chị gái à... Thảo nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.79,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{She replied!}Chị ấy trả lời rồi!
