Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:16.34,Sign_Basic,Message Sign,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\c&H394932&\3c&HA7F9CE&\shad0\frx8\fry352\pos(296.667,202)\frz331.1}{...You sure\Nyou don't want one?}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.34,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I actually sent that...}Mình gửi mất rồi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:20.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And now if he says he wants a picture, \NI should probably send one.}Và nếu em ấy nói muốn thì phải gửi thôi...
