Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.11,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Huh? All of a sudden...}Ủa? Mà sao lại...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:39.20,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm feeling really embarrassed!}xấu hổ thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:42.45,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Sending someone else a selfie like this...}Gửi ảnh tự sướng cho ai đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:46.73,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Who even does that \Nunless you're going out already?!}Đáng ra chỉ có ai đang hẹn hò mới làm thôi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:52.55,Italics,Shiori,0,0,0,,{He's gonna say he wants one!}Em ấy nói muốn kìa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.63,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{"I'm busy, so I'll be back later!"}Em đang bận nên tí em gọi lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:02.39,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I'm partly relieved and partly frustrated! \NWhy am I so conflicted?!}Sao mình lại vừa thấy nhẹ nhõm lại vừa thất vọng vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:08.62,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{You had better apologize \Nto Senpai for bothering her.}Tí nữa chị lo mà xin lỗi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:09.65,Main,Yutaka,0,0,0,,{Consider it done!}Đã rõ.
