Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.06,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Shinozaki-san.}Shinozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:07.12,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,Chào buổi sáng.{Good morning, Shinozaki-san!}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:09.87,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{G-G-Good morning.}C-Chào chị!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.18,0:19:13.38,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Um... I'm sorry about \Nhow my sister acted yesterday.}Em xin lỗi về chuyện đêm qua...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.70,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{It's quite all right.}Không sao mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.27,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{And... about that picture you mentioned...}Về tấm ảnh mà em nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:23.01,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{If it's not too much trouble, \NI'd be really glad to receive one!}Nếu được em muốn có một tấm!
