Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:21.16,Main,Shiori,0,0,0,,{Are you nervous, Shinozaki-san?}Em lo lắng hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:21.89,Main,Shinozaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah!}Vâng.
